'''''Polyhedron'' 126''' was a roleplaying magazine from [[October]] of [[1997]]. It contained many roleplaying articles, including advice for a ''[[Star Wars]]'' LARP. The article was called "[[Vignette Characters & Scenes for Star Wars: Live Action Adventures]]" and was written by [[Paul Sudlow]]. Like all supplements printed in ''[[Polyhedron]]'' prior to [[2002]], the article is considered ambiguously [[canon]].

